Jeremy Irons Brings Francis Bacon's Words to Life

SothebysTV / YouTube
As Francis Bacon said, "Everything I do goes into painting." In this short video, Academy Award-winning actor Jeremy Irons brings to life excerpts from the artist's interviews with David Sylvester and reveals Bacon's own thoughts..

Legendary Filmmaker John Waters On the Audacity of Cy Twombly

SothebysTV / YouTube
What is like to live with a work by post-war master Cy Twombly? According to legendary filmmaker John Waters, it's "great because every day when you pass it you think of his nerve. The audacity of him doing this."

Picasso Ceramics

Coinciding with our May Impressionist & Modern Art and Post-War and Contemporary Art sales, Christie's presents an online auction of ceramics by Pablo Picasso. Featuring 88 lots, with estimates ranging from $800 to $80,000, our Picasso Ceramics online sale offers a diverse selection of statement pieces.
